<h2 id="show-list-of-screen-running-in-background">Show List of Screen Running in Background</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">stechalon</span><span class="vi">@localhost</span> <span class="o">~</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">screen</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">ls</span>
<span class="no">There</span> <span class="n">are</span> <span class="n">screens</span> <span class="ss">on:
        </span><span class="mi">3784</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">top</span>        <span class="p">(</span><span class="no">Attached</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="mi">2077</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">pts</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">localhost</span>    <span class="p">(</span><span class="no">Detached</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mi">2</span> <span class="no">Sockets</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="sr">/var/</span><span class="n">run</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">screen</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="no">S</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">alon</span><span class="o">.</span></code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="detach-screen">Detach Screen</h2>
<p>Type <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">screen -d ID</code> so that this can be reattach in future.</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">stechalon</span><span class="vi">@localhost</span> <span class="o">~</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">screen</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">d</span> <span class="mi">3784</span></code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="reattach-screen">Reattach Screen</h2>
<p>Type <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">screen -r ID</code> for the screen which was previously detached.</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">stechalon</span><span class="vi">@localhost</span> <span class="o">~</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">screen</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">r</span> <span class="mi">2077</span></code></pre></figure>

